Arduino is very cool thing.

You can use it to program the device.

Steps to do:
1. Start Arduino.
2. Take the device.
3. Connect the device to compurter (usin USB wire - to the USB port).
4. Write program on Arduino (can use the samples available, if wize, could download some more samples).
5. Write program to the device (via USB wire - keep it connected).
6. And you have device with program, good achievement.

Useful info on Arduino could be found here:
https://www.arduino.cc/en/software

